cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.CY, cs.SE, cs.DS

The paper title suggests that it is related to cryptography and security (cs.CR). The authors propose a new attribute-based signature scheme with policy and endorsement mechanism, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and cyber security (cs.CY). The paper also discusses the implementation of the proposed scheme, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and data structures (cs.DS).
